OL,3,CWhat is a Passion play and why was it
OL,4,Cbeing performed in Hampshire?
OL,6,FReport by ITV Meridian reporter Sally
OL,7,FSimmonds
OL,9,FTheatre came to the streets of Havant
OL,10,Fin Hampshire today as a Passion play
OL,11,Fwas performed in the town centre to
OL,12,Fmark Easter.
OL,14,FThe story of the trial, death and
OL,15,Fresurrection of Jesus took place on a
OL,16,Fmakeshift stage in the high street.
OL,18,FThe idea is to attract passers by and
OL,19,Finteract with the audience and bring
OL,20,Fthe story to life.
