OL,3,CWhat is a Passion play and why was it
OL,4,Cbeing performed in Hampshire?
OL,6,FThe viewing of and participation in
OL,7,FPassion Plays is a traditional part of
OL,8,FLent.
OL,10,FThe production company, Havant Passion
OL,11,FPlay, is made up of amateur actors
OL,12,Ffrom around Havant, and has previously
OL,13,Fstaged Passion Plays in Havant Park in
OL,14,Fprevious years.
