OL,3,CWhat is a Passion play and why was it
OL,4,Cbeing performed in Hampshire?
OL,6,FCarolyn Owens, head of productions at
OL,7,FHavant Passion Play said: "Easter is a
OL,8,Ftraditional time to perform a Passion
OL,9,FPlay, and we are thrilled to be
OL,10,Fworking with Havant Borough Council,
OL,11,Fthe market and town centre churches to
OL,12,Fbring this story to life at the heart
OL,13,Fof the community. It is a fabulous
OL,14,Fopportunity for us all."
