OL,3,CWhat is a Passion play and why was it
OL,4,Cbeing performed in Hampshire?
OL,6,FThe production's director is
OL,7,Fprofessional actor and director James
OL,8,FBurke-Dunsmore, who for many years
OL,9,Fportrayed Jesus each Good Friday in
OL,10,FTrafalgar Square, and also at summer
OL,11,Fproductions of 'The Life of Christ' in
OL,12,Fthe near Guildford.
